videos.description: Mikal Bridges enters the game for Villanova and immediately throws down a posterization dunk against Purdue.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bridges announces his presence with monster dunk) 2016/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bridges announces his presence with monster dunk

videos.description: Darryl Reynolds follows up the Villanova miss and hammers home the putback dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Reynolds flies in for putback dunk) 2016/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Reynolds flies in for putback dunk

videos.description: Kris Jenkins buries a long 3-pointer that looks eerily similar to the one he hit to win last season's National Championship game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jenkins pulls up from a familiar spot) 2016/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jenkins pulls up from a familiar spot

videos.description: P.J. Thompson gets the pass and miraculously gets his half-court heave to fall just before the first-half buzzer sounds against Villanova.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (P.J. Thompson hits incredible half-court buzzer beater) 2016/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: P.J. Thompson hits incredible half-court buzzer beater

videos.description: Purdue's Caleb Swanigan dazzles with a spinning, no-look pass to Vincent Edwards for the uncontested layup against Villanova.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Swanigan does his best Magic Johnson impersonation for Purdue) 2016/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Swanigan does his best Magic Johnson impersonation for Purdue
